          "settings": {
            "heading": "Benefits",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>Ultimate Moisture: </strong>No more chapped lips as <a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/\">mad honey</a> and essential oils team up to repair, hydrate, and protect.</li><li><strong>Silky Smooth: </strong>Olive oil and apricot oil work their magic for soft, kissable lips.</li><li><strong>Weather Shield: </strong>Protects your lips from dryness, no matter the season.</li><li><strong>Lip Primer: </strong>Its creamy texture preps lips for lipstick, ensuring a flawless application.</li><li><strong>Night Therapy: </strong>Use as a PM lip mask to wake up with supple, refreshed lips.</li><li><strong>Gentle Exfoliation: </strong>Grapeseed oil removes dead skin cells, leaving lips fresh and plum</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_PLWqqY": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Directions",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<ul><li>Apply a small amount of lip balm evenly to your lips using clean fingers or directly from the tube.</li><li>Reapply as needed throughout the day, especially in dry or cold weather.</li><li>For intense hydration, use before bed as an overnight lip mask.</li><li>Can be used as a base before applying lipstick for a smoother finish.</li><li>Store in a cool, dry place to maintain texture and consistency.</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
