    "faq_fFAwqm": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_XEPM9x": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What makes Mad Honey Lip Balms different?",
            "answer": "<p>Our Mad Honey Lip Balms are made from rare, potent mad honey beeswax, providing deep hydration and nourishment. Formulated with natural oils and essential ingredients, they protect and rejuvenate your lips, leaving them soft, smooth, and healthy.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_bJtL4k": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are your ingredients organic?",
            "answer": "<p>We choose organic, natural, high-quality ingredients like olive oil, grapeseed oil, apricot oil, and mad honey beeswax for the best care for the lops with minimal additives.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_cU9Bya": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I have a honey allergy, can I still use honey balm?",
            "answer": "<p>We recommend doing a patch test before use to check for any allergic reactions, but it’s safest to consult your doctor if you're uncertain.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_B7TK9g": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do the different flavors of lip balm provide additional benefits?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! Each flavor offers a unique benefit. For example, Wild Mint provides a cooling effect, Orange offers a refreshing burst of citrus, and Green Tea offers hydrating and antioxidant properties. Each adds a little something extra to keep your lips nourished and pampered.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_UzHYFV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How often should I apply lip balm throughout the day?",
            "answer": "<p>You can apply lip balm as often as needed, especially when your lips feel dry or chapped. Reapplying in the morning, throughout the day, and before bed will help maintain soft and hydrated lips.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_6JXXi9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is Mad Honey Lip Balm suitable for all lip types, including sensitive lips?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, our Mad Honey Lip Balm is gentle and suitable for all lip types, including sensitive lips. Our natural ingredients are soothing and protective, making it ideal for sensitive skin, but we recommend a quick patch test to ensure its effects. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_3UNgd6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is the best way to apply lip balm?",
            "answer": "<p>For best results, apply a generous amount of lip balm directly from the tube or with clean fingers. Reapply as needed throughout the day for lasting moisture, and use it overnight as a lip mask for extra hydration. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_YjkEjC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where are your products made?",
            "answer": "<p>Our products are handmade in small batches by a women’s group in Nepal. We source our mad honey and beeswax directly from the Nepalese Himalayas. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_Gd6WJK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are your products preservative-free?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, our Mad Honey Lip Balms are free from artificial preservatives. We use natural ingredients to keep your lips nourished and protected without the need for harmful additives.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_P9NyGb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is mad honey wax good for your lips?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! Mad honey beeswax is packed with natural benefits, including moisturizing and protecting your lips from dryness.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
